{"tid":895193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"姚思榮：旅遊界商場商議包車接送旅客　籲勿搞光復行動免添煩添亂","createTime":"2018-11-09T04:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T04:36:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ab2a2b87907674922b3201c2d0b53767a64c3c","tid":895193,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181109/s00001/9ea8f3ea9bd08d8e77b4c0f9f4969f8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181109%2Fs00001%2F9ea8f3ea9bd08d8e77b4c0f9f4969f8e.jpg&h=f891faf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為紓緩港珠澳大橋通車後的東涌人流，運輸署將縮短旅遊巴到大橋香港口岸停車區上客的申請時間至1日，並可接載內地旅客直接到市區主要購物點。立法會旅遊界議員姚思榮透露，了解到業界正與購物商場商討，計劃由津貼包車形式，接送旅客直到商場，當中黃金海岸、新田購物城均在考慮之列，預料最快兩周後實施安排。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有本土派團體計劃周末舉行「光復東涌」行動，姚思榮表示不希望有類似情況發生，因為此舉既影響香港形象，且政府、業界等正為紓緩東涌市中心壓力而努力，呼籲示威者不要再「添煩添亂」。<br />\n<br />\n至於即將到來的周末東涌居民應如何自處，姚思榮表示不必如此緊張，因政府、業界等持份者都非常重視東涌情況，是否得以解決只是時間問題，呼籲居民諒解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181109/s00001/1541730074402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181109%2Fs00001%2F1541730074402&d=G9rguUQjZKtPcM8sTPrYkWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=7ff4b6e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181109%2Fs00001%2F1541730074402&h=e0046989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181109/s00001/1541730074402</a>"},{"pid":"f00c42c2b301e6797a1447772c78b9c7aec0fa53","tid":895193,"uid":4174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:11:16.000Z","msg":"賣豬仔坐個幾鐘車去新田購物城 仲要唔知幾多間鋪開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24efcdf6eedf3242daa663270b6d6813b6a7bff3","tid":895193,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:12:11.000Z","msg":"原位癌擴散"},{"pid":"c158deff923d9c12826828bdd14627c6f5020b29","tid":895193,"uid":163801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n至於即將到來的周末東涌居民應如何自處，姚思榮表示不必如此緊張，因政府、業界等持份者都非常重視東涌情況，<span style=\"color: red;\">是否得以解決只是時間問題，呼籲居民諒解。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181109/s00001/1541730074402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181109%2Fs00001%2F1541730074402&d=G9rguUQjZKtPcM8sTPrYkWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=7ff4b6e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181109%2Fs00001%2F1541730074402&h=e0046989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181109/s00001/1541730074402</a></blockquote><br />\n捱多四五七年, 時間問題咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71b878a4b49cc1e1606f5578814637fc54b23e3","tid":895193,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"嗱，我就唔支持光復嘅，最好每日幾十萬，甚至過百萬蝗蟲嚟Dont衝同閪鳩窿，區區都有大量蝗蟲周圍走周圍踎同屙屎屙尿就最完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}